really early in Great Tables, I do feel like it was almost kind of the perfect time

00:07:27.220 --> 00:07:32.100
to your point that we could tell Polars they have this thing called lazy expressions.

00:07:32.899 --> 00:07:38.739
And we could tell them like, hey, we think that if we just take the job of displaying tables and

00:07:38.739 --> 00:07:44.420
making them pretty, we can just use your lazy expressions to make it really easy to say like

00:07:44.420 --> 00:07:50.980
highlight a specific row, say like the row where some value is its maximum in the table.

00:07:51.859 --> 00:07:58.899
Like, we can do that with your expressions. And like you can focus on how could people

