and it's really gassed up by the problem, it can be kind of tricky to keep maintaining all these

00:08:49.780 --> 00:08:57.859
pieces. Yeah, yeah. And one issue that I've seen is that you also end up with a tightly coupled

00:08:57.859 --> 00:09:03.700
